---
// Testimonials Section based on crawled 10botics.com data
// This was originally an Elementor testimonial carousel widget
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        客戶評價
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        聽聽學校和學生對我們服務的評價
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">陳校長</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">天保民學校</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
          "10Botics 的課程設計非常適合我們的學生，讓他們在輕鬆愉快的氛圍中學習 STEM 知識。"
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">馮耀宗老師</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">香港紅十字會甘迺迪中心</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
          "與 10Botics 合作讓我們的特教學生也能享受 STEM 教育的樂趣，效果超出預期。"
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">李老師</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">聖類斯中學</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
          "10Botics 的 AI 課程讓我們的學生對人工智能有了深入的認識，激發了他們的學習興趣。"
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">王主任</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">九龍華仁書院</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
          "STEM Day 活動非常成功，學生們都表示希望有更多類似的學習機會。"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 